    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>parsley </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Once done, remove the <strong>warmed naan</strong> from the <strong>toaster </strong>and add the <strong>berbere-spiced butter </strong>– this is your<strong> berbere-spiced butter naan</strong></p>",
