      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Ethiopian-style veggie wat </strong>in bowls and top with a <strong>soft-boiled</strong> <strong>egg half</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped parsley</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>berbere-spiced butter naan</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
